data.description: Step into Vintage Charm with this 1945-built 4-bedroom, 2-full bathroom home, spanning 2,333 sqft. of living space. Nestled on a convenient location, with a 0.32-acre lot, this residence beckons with original hardwood floors, lending character to every room.The Living Room is a focal point, featuring a wood-burning fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings. Entertain with style in the formal dining area, complemented by spacious bedrooms that offer comfort and versatility. Beyond, discover walk-out basement space, providing additional room for recreation or relaxation. Outside, the large backyard completes the picture, offering an ideal space for outdoor enjoyment. Capture the perfect blend of vintage allure and modern amenities in this well-appointed home.
